islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T18:14:11.000Z","msg":"唉  睇著直播完全訓唔著<br />\n聽朝一早就會衝出去開工<br />\n寧為玉碎 不為瓦全<br />\n岩先睇到有係理大既同學<br />\n係到做訪問<br />\n個個都話驚到喊哂出黎<br />\n我都忍唔著大喊左一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都覺得自己咩都幫唔到手<br />\n次次出去剩係識企後排<br />\n同去和理非<br />\n但今次真係好有決心聽日一早就衝出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班後生讀緊大學<br />\n大好光明前途<br />\n如果今晚發生咩事<br />\n我都唔想再忍<br />\n我好愛香港<br />\n都唔想香港變成咁<br />\n只希望奇蹟會出現香港<br />\n總有一日我地會係煲底相擁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"2032b4941de4362ccd53c73f7d4b6ae3ec40063d","tid":1731540,"uid":261384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T18:15:39.000Z","msg":"天救理大，捱過今晚我就戒打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcd50575399bbd4c76fc78cd4339959118ce841","tid":1731540,"uid":330084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T18:16:01.000Z","msg":"真係出唔到嘅,Twitter要人呀!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62da205815d1f574c36a7e087ffa723206824402","tid":1731540,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afcd50575399bbd4c76fc78cd4339959118ce841","tid":1731540,"uid":330084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T18:16:01.000Z","msg":"真係出唔到嘅,Twitter要人呀!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T18:19:12.000Z","msg":"推 搵人一齊過twitter幫手"},{"pid":"bbe5b8bdff9ae52f0c890e9d3152d42ce22c0c5e","tid":1731540,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2032b4941de4362